          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1688462397388-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> coated chicken </strong>to the pan and cook for 9-10 min on each side or until charred and cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
