    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>chopped pineapple</strong>, <strong>diced</strong> <strong>shallot</strong> and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>coriander</strong> in a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>pineapple salsa</strong></p>",
