    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Combine your<strong> mayo</strong> and <strong>reserved pineapple juice</strong> in a separate bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>pineapple mayo</strong></p>",
