      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, transfer it to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks - this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p><p>Return the <strong>pulled free range chicken</strong> to the pan with the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and cook over a medium-high heat for 1-2 min or until fragrant – this is your <strong>Caribbean-style free range chicken</strong></p>",
